<a name="layered"></a>
<b>My customers need to tell me more about their car, like engine size, bed size, door length, seat type, wheel size, how does that work?</b>
<br />
The Make Model Year search <a href="http://vehiclefits.com/about/search.php">integrates with layered navigation</a>. Magento's <a href="http://www.magentocommerce.com/product/features/catalog-browsing/view">layered navigation</a> is a multi-faceted filter, allowing your products to be filtered by "attributes", such as color, size, or anything you set up. Your products, lets say wheels, should each have an attribute like size. After the user selects their vehicle the user will be able to enter the size wheel they are looking for.
