<a name="one_by_one"></a><b>So do I have to set up each vehicle and product "one by one"?</b>
<br />
<p>By no means would that be required, as it would take too much time! We offer a  <a href="http://vehiclefits.com/databases.php">100,000+ record <i>make/model/year</i> &amp; <i>make/model/trim/year</i> database</a>. There are also multiple formats for <a href="http://vehiclefits.com/about/data.php">importing your existing data</a>.</p>

